# ScoreStage Privacy Policy

Effective date: April 7, 2026  
Operator: okeke  
Contact: kiyohbimbow@gmail.com  
Website: https://kiyohbimbo.gumroad.com/

ScoreStage ("the App") is designed for reading, organizing, backing up, restoring, and migrating sheet music from MobileSheets. The App is intended to work primarily offline and does not collect personal information for advertising or behavioral analytics.

## 1. Information We Collect

### 1.1 Information collected automatically
The App does not automatically collect personal information or device information for analytics, advertising, or data sharing with third parties.

### 1.2 Information you save or import
Depending on your actions, the App may store or import the following information locally on your device:

- Sheet music files
- Annotations, handwriting, and drawing data
- Bookmarks
- Setlists
- Display and control settings
- Backup data
- Data migrated from MobileSheets
  - score information
  - annotations
  - setlists
  - related settings

These items are processed and stored primarily on your device.  
The App does not send these files or data to our servers without your explicit action.

### 1.3 Information you send when contacting support
If you contact us, we may receive your email address and the content of your message.  
We use this information only to respond to your inquiry and provide support.

## 2. How We Use Information

We use the information described above to:

- Display, read, and manage sheet music
- Save annotations and bookmarks
- Manage setlists
- Back up and restore data
- Migrate data from MobileSheets
- Save user settings
- Respond to support requests
- Improve the App and fix issues

## 3. Sharing of Information

We do not share your information with third parties except where required by law.  
We do not send personal information or usage history to advertising providers or external analytics providers.

## 4. Storage and Retention

Data handled by the App is stored primarily on your device or in a location you explicitly choose.  
If you create backups or export files, you are responsible for managing the destination where those files are stored.

## 5. Permissions

The App may use device file access features to read or save files that you select.  
Those permissions are used only to the extent necessary to provide the App's features.

## 6. Children's Privacy

The App is a general-purpose sheet music viewer and is not directed to children under 13.  
We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

## 7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.  
If we make material changes, we will notify you through the App or by publishing an updated policy page.

